@startuml state-payout
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam stateFontSize 12

title Payout State Machine

[*] --> Initiated : Committee approves\nassistance request

Initiated --> LimitsValidated : Per-event, annual,\nand frequency limits pass
Initiated --> Failed : Limits exceeded

LimitsValidated --> FundsReserved : Trust account balance\nsufficient; funds held
LimitsValidated --> Failed : Insufficient\ntrust balance

FundsReserved --> Processing : Payment dispatched\nto gateway

Processing --> Completed : Gateway confirms\nsuccessful deposit
Processing --> Failed : Gateway reports\npayment failure

Failed --> Initiated : Admin triggers\nmanual retry

Completed --> Reversed : Fraud detected or\nclawback required

Completed --> [*]
Reversed --> [*]

state Initiated : Entry / Create payout record\nEntry / Notify member
state LimitsValidated : Entry / Log limit check result
state FundsReserved : Entry / Hold funds with\noptimistic lock
state Processing : Entry / Record gateway reference\nEntry / Notify member
state Completed : Entry / Confirm withdrawal\nEntry / Record FundTransaction\nEntry / Notify member
state Failed : Entry / Release reserved funds\nEntry / Log failure reason\nEntry / Notify member
state Reversed : Entry / Credit trust account\nEntry / Record reversal transaction\nEntry / Notify compliance

@enduml
